### Test Authentication Endpoints

### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:5074/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User"
}

### Login with credentials
POST http://localhost:5074/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "rememberMe": false
}

### Validate token (requires Authorization header)
GET http://localhost:5074/api/auth/validate
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Logout (requires Authorization header)
POST http://localhost:5074/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Refresh token
POST http://localhost:5074/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}